feeds the Bunch-Kaufman stability consumer directly. -/
theorem higham11_4_bunch_kaufman_stability_of_first_stage_recursive_higham_const_bounds
    (n s : ℕ) (hn : 0 < n) (hs_pos : 0 < s) (hs_le : s ≤ n)
